OL,5, The BBC's director general Tim Davie   
OL,6, has announced that the corporation will
OL,7, explore how to reform the licence fee. 
OL,9,FDavie said the BBC will "proactively   
OL,10,Fresearch how to reform the licence fee 
OL,11,Fpost-2028", looking at its scope, how  
OL,12,Fprogressive it is and its enforcement. 
OL,14,FIn a speech on Tuesday, Davie said "it 
OL,15,Fis right to ask fundamental questions  
OL,16,Fabout its longevity".                  
OL,18,FBut he added "we should be... cautious 
OL,19,Fabout unpicking a multi-genre BBC that 
OL,20,Fleads the market."                     
